Monstrosity of a script that will run the follower linters using on files
git status says have been modified

* flake8
* tslint
* jshint
* csslint

For JSHint it will also adding missing semi colons automatically.

It will also check python scripts and javascript files from print() and console.log
statements respectively. I have a habit of forgetting to delete them when I
use them as placeholders
